snippet.title: My Suika - Watermelon Game - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
A fun watermelon merge puzzle game!

Think you can get 3000 points in this addictive watermelon puzzle game?

Combine various matching fruits to help Kyo gather watermelons! Unlock new game modes and new fruit skins by obtaining high scores. Compete against other players on the global leaderboards!

Developed by Watashi Games
NOTE: This is a clone of Suika Game, which was released on mobile.
